Package: glmmfields
Type: Package
Title: GLMMs with Robust Random Fields for Spatiotemporal Modelling
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(c("Sean", "C."), "Anderson", email = "sean@seananderson.ca", 
      role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person(c("Eric", "J."), "Ward", role = "aut"))
Description: Implements Bayesian spatiotemporal models that allow for extreme
    spatial deviations through time. 'glmmfields' uses a predictive process 
    approach with random fields implemented through a multivariate-t distribution
    instead of the usual multivariate normal. Sampling is conducted with 'Stan'.
License: GPL (>=3)
Encoding: UTF-8
